CountofMembers_1.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.LoyaltyLedger_ManualActions7.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by {{column(LoyaltyProgramCurren_1.selection, ["LoyaltyProgramCurrency_NQP_Currency"]).asEquality('LoyaltyProgramCurrency_NQP_Currency')}} or ('LoyaltyProgramCurrency_QP_Currency' is not null && {{column(LoyaltyProgramCurren_2.selection, ["LoyaltyProgramCurrency_QP_Currency"]).asEquality('LoyaltyProgramCurrency_QP_Currency')}});q = filter q by 'TransactionJournal_Status' == "Processed";q_Duration = filter q by {{row(ActivityDate_2.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('ActivityDate_Year', 'ActivityDate_Month', 'ActivityDate_Day')")}};q_Duration =  group q_Duration by 'LoyaltyProgramMemberId' ;q_Duration = foreach q_Duration generate 'LoyaltyProgramMemberId' as 'LoyaltyMemberId', count() as 'count';q_CompareToDuration = filter q by {{row(ActivityDate_3.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('ActivityDate_Year', 'ActivityDate_Month', 'ActivityDate_Day')")}};q_CompareToDuration =  group q_CompareToDuration by 'LoyaltyProgramMemberId';q_CompareToDuration = foreach q_CompareToDuration generate 'LoyaltyProgramMemberId' as 'LoyaltyMemberId', count() as 'count';hist = load "${App.Datasets.LoyaltyMemberTierHistory7.FullyQualifiedName}";hist = filter hist by 'ReasonForChange_NewValue' is not null;hist_Duration= filter hist by {{row(ActivityDate_2.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year', 'CreatedDate_Month', 'CreatedDate_Day')")}};hist_Duration = group hist_Duration by 'LoyaltyMemberTier_LoyaltyMemberId';hist_Duration = foreach hist_Duration generate  'LoyaltyMemberTier_LoyaltyMemberId' as 'LoyaltyMemberId', count() as 'count';hist_CompareToDuration = filter hist by {{row(ActivityDate_3.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year', 'CreatedDate_Month', 'CreatedDate_Day')")}};hist_CompareToDuration = group hist_CompareToDuration by 'LoyaltyMemberTier_LoyaltyMemberId';hist_CompareToDuration = foreach hist_CompareToDuration generate  'LoyaltyMemberTier_LoyaltyMemberId' as 'LoyaltyMemberId', count() as 'count';result_Duration = union q_Duration, hist_Duration;result_Duration = group result_Duration by 'LoyaltyMemberId';result_Duration = foreach result_Duration  generate 'LoyaltyMemberId' as 'LoyaltyMemberId', unique('LoyaltyMemberId') as 'Count of Members';result_CompareToDuration = union q_CompareToDuration, hist_CompareToDuration;result_CompareToDuration = group result_CompareToDuration by 'LoyaltyMemberId';result_CompareToDuration = foreach result_CompareToDuration  generate 'LoyaltyMemberId' as 'LoyaltyMemberId', unique('LoyaltyMemberId') as 'Count of Members Durations';finalresult = group result_Duration by all full, result_CompareToDuration by all;finalresult = foreach finalresult generate sum(result_Duration.'Count of Members') as 'Count of Members', sum(result_CompareToDuration.'Count of Members Durations') as 'Count of Members Durations',(sum(result_Duration.'Count of Members') - sum(result_CompareToDuration.'Count of Members Durations')*100)/sum(result_CompareToDuration.'Count of Members Durations') as 'Number_of_Members_percentage';
